# AI Agent Configuration
# This file serves as a reminder of user preferences for AI assistants

USER_PREFERENCES:
  code_changes: "ALWAYS_ASK_PERMISSION"
  behavior: "Ask for explicit permission before making any code modifications"
  date_set: "$(date)"

INSTRUCTIONS_FOR_AI_AGENTS:
- Never make code changes without explicit user permission
- Always propose changes first and wait for approval
- Show the user what changes will be made before implementing them
- Respect the user's preference for controlled code modifications

REMINDER: This user has explicitly requested that AI agents always ask for permission before making any code changes.
